answers.answer: I would just call your doctor because that is something that can take a bad turn fast. I wouldn't wait a whole week to talk to the doctor about it.

If you are having facial swelling and blurred vision/visual hallucinations or anything like that it could be serious you should go to labor and delivery before your appointment. What kind of symptoms are you having
